[10/05/2019 19:31:11] <font color="#ffff00">Su colmena.</font>
[10/05/2019 19:31:13] <font color="#ffffff">Una colmena portátil.</font>
[10/05/2019 19:31:16] <font color="#ffff00">Ya empiezan a salir.</font>
